reviewText: Dr. Guliuzza informs you on just what a miracle it takes for pregnancy to occur. Though my mother was a biology teacher I'm sure she knew very few of the many details that the doctor details. He presents this information in a humorous and very interesting manner and throughout he ascribes the glory to the ultimate Creator. I have seen this several times but had to get my own DVD to share with friends and my children and grandchildren.
What an amazing and true look at babies from a medical doctor's perspective
very interesting and informative, the human race is an incredible design.
Truly informative and a great read for understanding biblical creationism!
